12 §189.1. Legislative findings; purpose
13 A. Legislative Findings.
14 The legislature hereby finds and declares all of the following:
15 (1) Career and technical education is foundational to Louisiana's
16 workforce development, economic competitiveness, and educational goals, and
17 a coherent, high-quality career and technical education system is essential to
